Data and parsing for government types
Data and parsing for citizens
Particular requirements for buildings, wonders, and minor wonders


Agricultural  : Plantations and similar
Industrious   : Mines and quarries
Expansionist  : Outpost (city founded by military units)
Religious     : Monasteries
Militaristic  : Forts and similar
Scientific    : 
Commercial    : Trading posts
Seafaring     : Shipyard


Where our state ends up: 

Global for all civilizations: 
 - Wonder array (built)

Per-civilization:
 - Tech array
 - Minor-wonder array (built)

Per city:
 - Building array (built)
 - Unit array (trainable)
